The advisory board shall be composed of the following members appointed by the Governor as specified:
Two (2) members selected from a list of three (3) submitted by the Kentucky Animal Control Association;
Two (2) members selected from a list of three (3) submitted by the Kentucky Veterinary Medical Association;
Two (2) members selected from a list of three (3) submitted by the Kentucky Farm Bureau;
Two (2) members selected from a list of three (3) submitted by the Kentucky Association of Counties;
Two (2) members selected from a list of three (3) submitted by the Kentucky Houndsmen Association; and
Two (2) members selected from a list of three (3) submitted by the Kentucky League of Cities.
